{"article_id":"Jk6B6WuNvqCGGfjh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump has called the press","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"\" the enemy of the people , \" \" very dangerous & sick \" and , of course , \" fake news. \"","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Now newspapers are fighting back .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"More than 300 newspapers across the US ran editorials Thursday","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"promoting freedom of the press , part of an effort","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"coordinated by the Boston Globe .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"Participants include large newspapers like the New York Times and small local publications with circulations as low as 4,000 ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"and the Globe encouraged editorial boards to participate","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"regardless of their political point of view .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"The Times has published a list of the participating papers .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"The principle of a free press ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"the Globe ' s editorial board wrote ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"\" has protected journalists at home","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and served as a model for free nations abroad .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Today it is under serious threat . \"","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"In a recent poll ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"the Globe noted ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"48 percent of Republicans and 29 percent of Americans overall agreed with Trump","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"that the news media is the enemy of the people .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Forty-three percent of Republicans and 26 percent of Americans said","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"the president should be able to close news outlets for bad behavior .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"\" The greatness of America is dependent on the role of a free press","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"to speak the truth to the powerful , \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"the board wrote .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"\" To label the press ' the enemy of the people ' is as un-American","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"as it is dangerous to the civic compact","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"we have shared for more than two centuries . \"","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Editorial boards around the country added their own words on Thursday .","depth":4},{"id":28,"text":"A free press builds the foundation for democracy .","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Citizens depend on honest , independent media for accurate information","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"they need","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"about their government , their elected leaders and their institutions .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"That is just as important in Tampa Bay and in communities across the nation","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"as it is in Washington ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"and the Times takes that responsibility seriously .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"We are , at the Sun-Times , the enemy of unchecked authority and undeserved privilege .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"We are the enemy of self-entitlement .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"We are the enemy of the notion","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that the only way up is to hold somebody else down .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"If you haven ' t already ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"please subscribe to your local papers .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Praise them","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"when you think","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"they ' ve done a good job","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"and criticize them","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"when you think","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"they could do better .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"We ' re all in this together .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"On bitter cold January nights , we ' re the people ' s eyes and ears at city , town , village and school board meetings .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"We tell the stories of our communities , from the fun of a county fair to the despair","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"a family faces","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"when a loved one is killed .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"We are always by your side .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"We shop the same stores ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"attend the same churches","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"and hike the same trails .","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"We struggle with daycare","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"and worry about paying for retirement .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"In our work as journalists , our first loyalty is to you .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"The president appeared to respond to the editorials on Twitter Thursday morning :","depth":4},{"id":60,"text":"THE FAKE NEWS MEDIA IS THE OPPOSITION PARTY .","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"It is very bad for our Great Country ....","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"BUT WE ARE WINNING !","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"August 16 , 2018","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"The Boston Globe ,","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"which was sold to the the Failing New York Times for 1.3 BILLION DOLLARS","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"( plus 800 million dollars in losses & investment ) ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"or 2.1 BILLION DOLLARS ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"was then sold by the Times for 1 DOLLAR .","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"Now the Globe is in COLLUSION with other papers on free press .","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"PROVE IT !","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"August 16 , 2018","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":151,"left":134,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":85,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":78,"right":84,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":77,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":84,"left":80,"right":83,"relation":"elab